      "parameters": {
        "content": "## INPUT CONTRACT (Execute Workflow Trigger)\n\n`action` (string): `ensureAndWrite|ensureSheet|writeRows` (default `ensureAndWrite`)\n`session_sheet_id` or `sheetId` (string): existing sheet ID\n`session_sheet_name` or `sheetName` (string): sheet title when creating (default `book-review-assets`)\n`sheetTabName` (string): tab name (default `assets`)\n`session_folder_id` or `targetFolderId` (string): Drive folder to move sheet into\n`session_sheet_rows` or `sheetRows` (2D array): data rows to write at `A1`\n\n### Behavior flags (auto by Normalize Request)\n- `shouldEnsure`, `shouldWrite`, `shouldMove`\n- `shouldCreateSheet`, `shouldCallWriteApi`\n- `missingSheetIdForWrite`\n\n### Result keys\n`status`, `sheetId`, `sheetUrl`, `session_sheet_id`, `session_sheet_url`, `session_sheet_create_status_code`, `session_sheet_update_status_code`.",
